role_description: An Ansible role that installs Google Assistant for Desktop on nearly any system
role_description_full_overview: [Google Assistant for Desktop](https://github.com/Melvin-Abraham/Google-Assistant-Unofficial-Desktop-Client) is a cross-platform unofficial Google Assistant Client for Desktop.
